data.description: Welcome to your dream woodland retreat! This stunning home, nestled on 1.327 acres, offers the perfect blend of luxury and tranquility. Step inside to discover a meticulously crafted interior, featuring LVP hardwood-style flooring throughout the open-concept main floor. The custom kitchen boasts granite countertops, a large island with bar stool seating, and ample pantry storage, making it ideal for both everyday living and entertaining guests.     Relax in the spacious family room, or utilize the separate formal dining room, which can easily double as a home office. Upstairs, you'll find a generously sized master bedroom with two walk-in closets and a luxurious master bathroom complete with a large walk-in shower, dual vanities, and a water closet. Additionally, the second floor includes two secondary bedrooms, a full bathroom with dual vanities, a convenient laundry room, and a large finished bonus room, offering endless possibilities for customization.     Outside, a new black fence adds privacy and charm, while the property's boundaries extend beyond, providing ample room to explore and enjoy the natural surroundings. Plus, with a whole-home water filtration system and reverse osmosis, you can rest assured knowing that the water throughout the house is of the highest quality.   Don't miss your chance to own this like-new home, built in 2021, where every detail has been thoughtfully designed to enhance both style and functionality. Experience the epitome of modern living in your own woodland oasis!
